raw_meta_yaml:
# yaml-language-server: $schema=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/prefix-dev/recipe-format/main/schema.json
schema_version: 1

context:
  version: "0.2.15"

package:
  name: ruamel.yaml.clib
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/r/ruamel.yaml.clib/ruamel_yaml_clib-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 46e4cc8c43ef6a94885f72512094e482114a8a706d3c555a34ed4b0d20200600

build:
  number: 1
  script:
    - cythonize _ruamel_yaml.pyx
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation --disable-pip-version-check

requirements:
  build:
    - ${{ compiler("c") }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - cython
        - python
  host:
    - cython
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - script:
      - python -c "from importlib.util import find_spec; assert find_spec('_ruamel_yaml')"
  - downstream: ruamel.yaml

about:
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: C version of reader, parser and emitter for ruamel.yaml derived from libyaml
  homepage: https://pypi.org/project/ruamel.yaml.clib
  repository: https://sourceforge.net/projects/ruamel-yaml-clib

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
    - mbargull
    - ocefpaf
